{"tid":947893,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦唔著求教","createTime":"2018-12-19T15:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T01:57:35.000Z","uid":98502,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6be398a299edb18a8fbc179c2cf7c116e2d67935","tid":947893,"uid":98502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:21:39.000Z","msg":"請問各位，我部腦一直用黎開android模擬器掛game，前日突然死機開番發現花mon，之後不斷自動重新開機。咁我當時懷疑係死顯示卡，畢竟用左差唔多十年，就試下用onboard顯示卡著機，又得喎。咁我咪買過張二手返黎頂住檔先，一開始都用到，開左半個鐘都相安無事，之後唸住又掛過囉，食完飯番黎發現又死機，連bios畫面都見唔到，但睇番火牛風扇著，CPU風扇著，hdd著，顯示卡風扇著，但就係boot唔起，之後全部拆著，就剩番cpu著機，都係唔得，手痕換埋粒底板電餅，著機又得番喎，再裝番晒又唔得，唉。請教各位咁樣係唔係死左老母板<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c87e6d57e1ddebdbe9ee81496a3ae0eff6c726","tid":947893,"uid":90083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"硬件傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b616de609850721e1bf4c4fb5394b590fb91bf","tid":947893,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:48:30.000Z","msg":"姐係呢家又著到， 但唔肯定之前咩問題？"},{"pid":"9c93a1f9393849d8d982f40b1aede9d7cb13dd14","tid":947893,"uid":98502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9b616de609850721e1bf4c4fb5394b590fb91bf","tid":947893,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:48:30.000Z","msg":"姐係呢家又著到， 但唔肯定之前咩問題？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"唔好意思1999，呢家就係死左，但唔知邊到死，我懷疑係老母板"},{"pid":"92b3bac84d9ae34dc2ff1633b96bae26eac8219a","tid":947893,"uid":55870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c93a1f9393849d8d982f40b1aede9d7cb13dd14","tid":947893,"uid":98502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9b616de609850721e1bf4c4fb5394b590fb91bf","tid":947893,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:48:30.000Z","